00:01:30,170 --> 00:01:33,754
 

22
00:01:34,414 --> 00:01:36,375
- I told you!
- Yes.

23
00:01:36,375 --> 00:01:37,855
An emergency!

24
00:01:37,855 --> 00:01:39,454
The woodshed's on fire!

25
00:01:39,454 --> 00:01:40,974
The woodshed's on fire?

26
00:01:40,974 --> 00:01:42,454
Move!

27
00:01:42,454 --> 00:01:43,935
- Come on!
- Go!

28
00:01:43,935 --> 00:01:45,935
Come on!

29
00:01:45,935 --> 00:01:50,054
Wait. This is a diversion.

30
00:01:50,054 --> 00:01:52,589
- Let's head to Zhenmei Pavilion.
- Alright.

31
00:01:52,589 --> 00:01:54,455
 
Let's go.

32
00:01:55,495 --> 00:01:57,455
Well...

33
00:01:57,455 --> 00:02:00,534
- What's happening?
- No idea.

34
00:02:31,414 --> 00:02:33,214
Stop!

35
00:02:48,655 --> 00:02:50,654
Why did he kill himself?

36
00:02:58,335 --> 00:03:00,334
What are you doing here?

37
00:03:00,935 --> 00:03:05,175
I came to retrieve my jade pendant
from Lady Tang. I never expected this.

38
00:03:05,175 --> 00:03:08,175
I saw him sneaking, so I followed him.

39
00:03:08,175 --> 00:03:12,175
Shockingly, he attacked me on sight.

40
00:03:14,335 --> 00:03:17,774
Xi Lou, they're drugged with knockout powder.

41
00:03:19,095 --> 00:03:22,665
Qiu served our family for years.

42
00:03:22,665 --> 00:03:27,334
Yet he's Power Gang's mole all along.

43
00:03:31,175 --> 00:03:34,814
Tell me what Qiu did today.

44
00:03:34,814 --> 00:03:38,895
He's a cleaner of the Sword Retreat.
Today, he went to the woodshed.

45
00:03:38,895 --> 00:03:40,895
He also helped Zhang water flowers.

46
00:03:40,895 --> 00:03:47,415
Someone set the woodshed on fire to draw us there.

47
00:04:07,974 --> 00:04:12,374
Father, Mother, he watered the flowers to poison.

48
00:04:12,374 --> 00:04:16,455
Deliver my order. Don't get water from the well!

49
00:04:16,455 --> 00:04:20,414
Go and check if the well water
is already contaminated.

50
00:04:20,414 --> 00:04:22,214
Yes.

51
00:04:24,135 --> 00:04:27,215
We only have one well.

52
00:04:27,215 --> 00:04:32,414
The well water is poisoned.
All of us are targeted.

53
00:04:32,414 --> 00:04:34,494
Oh no! I had someone get water from the well.

54
00:04:34,494 --> 00:04:37,414
I made soup with it
and sent it to Zhenmei Pavilion.

55
00:04:37,414 --> 00:04:39,214
What?

56
00:04:40,054 --> 00:04:41,854
Go!

57
00:04:49,050 --> 00:04:50,170
 
Master Zhang.

58
00:04:50,170 --> 00:04:52,974
Mr. Xiao, what brings you here?

59
00:04:52,974 --> 00:04:56,414
The well water is poisoned. The soup's lethal.

60
00:04:56,414 --> 00:04:58,214
Mr. Xiao.

61
00:05:09,655 --> 00:05:11,614
Don't worry.

62
00:05:11,614 --> 00:05:14,854
I've not eaten your soup yet.

63
00:05:14,854 --> 00:05:17,095
No more secrets then.

64
00:05:17,095 --> 00:05:19,575
Get them all here.

65
00:05:22,015 --> 00:05:25,695
Listen, this is Madam Wu.

66
00:05:27,455 --> 00:05:29,615
Greetings, Madam Wu.

67
00:05:30,575 --> 00:05:33,654
Nice to meet you all.

68
00:05:36,054 --> 00:05:38,815
Everyone, be seated.

69
00:05:38,815 --> 00:05:40,854
Thank you, Madam Wu.

70
00:05:46,135 --> 00:05:53,575
Madam Wu, these brave people
resist Power Gang alongside my family.

71
00:05:54,934 --> 00:05:58,815
When I hear of your valor against Power Gang,

72
00:05:58,815 --> 00:06:02,458
I can't sleep or eat comfortably here.

73
00:06:02,458 --> 00:06:08,534
I lost my appetite for the soup,
so I narrowly avoided death.

74
00:06:10,054 --> 00:06:13,255
Why seek refuge here, Madam?

75
00:06:13,255 --> 00:06:16,054
I planned to go to Xianren Pass to find my son.

76
00:06:16,054 --> 00:06:21,294
Unexpectedly, some people
intercepted me at Jinzhong.

77
00:06:21,294 --> 00:06:24,575
They demanded the Hero Token.

78
00:06:24,575 --> 00:06:30,734
Luckily, Mr. Xiao saved and sheltered me.

79
00:06:32,095 --> 00:06:35,414
Madam Wu, may I ask you a question?

80
00:06:35,414 --> 00:06:37,934
Forgive my presumption.

81
00:06:37,934 --> 00:06:39,054
Go ahead.

82
00:06:39,054 --> 00:06:42,015
You're not from the martial world.

83
00:06:42,015 --> 00:06:46,615
Why do they think you have the Hero Token?

84
00:06:49,294 --> 00:06:54,015
13 years ago, North Wasteland's troops came.

85
00:06:54,015 --> 00:06:56,695
They occupied our land

86
00:06:56,695 --> 00:06:59,135
and marched into Daxi.

87
00:06:59,775 --> 00:07:04,695
They pillaged and slaughtered our people.

88
00:07:05,374 --> 00:07:07,294
People were homeless.

89
00:07:07,294 --> 00:07:09,095
 Protect His Majesty! 

90
00:07:09,095 --> 00:07:11,374
The emperor was forced to flee.

91
00:07:11,374 --> 00:07:15,534
Daxi teetered on the brink of collapse.

92
00:07:21,414 --> 00:07:28,534
Back then, the sect leaders of Shaolin, Wudang,
and Emei gathered men.

93
00:07:28,534 --> 00:07:30,854
They forged the Hero Token with a celestial spar

94
00:07:30,854 --> 00:07:36,015
and took a blood oath together.

95
00:07:36,015 --> 00:07:38,854
 
Whoever saves Daxi

96
00:07:38,854 --> 00:07:42,335
shall receive this spar.

97
00:07:42,335 --> 00:07:46,654
One man achieved this.

98
00:07:48,215 --> 00:07:49,534
You mean Yan Kuang Tu?

99
00:07:49,534 --> 00:07:53,934
Yes, he broke into the North Wasteland's camp

100
00:07:53,934 --> 00:07:56,934
and killed 37 elite soldiers

101
00:07:56,934 --> 00:08:00,135
and nearly killed their commander.

102
00:08:19,095 --> 00:08:22,734
Thus, he had the Hero Token.

103
00:08:22,734 --> 00:08:27,014
But the martial circle hated his arrogance.

104
00:08:27,014 --> 00:08:33,135
He vanished after an ambush on Mount Wuxing.

105
00:08:34,415 --> 00:08:41,015
Until recently, a falcon took the token to me.

106
00:08:43,614 --> 00:08:45,654
So, Yan Kuang Tu

107
00:08:45,654 --> 00:08:50,014
intentionally gave the Hero Token to you?

108
00:08:50,014 --> 00:08:51,814
Exactly.

109
00:08:53,654 --> 00:08:59,734
Power Gang knew about that,

110
00:08:59,734 --> 00:09:02,055
so they hunted me down.

111
00:09:02,055 --> 00:09:06,735
Innocent blood spilled during the pursuit.

112
00:09:08,854 --> 00:09:13,575
Mr. Xiao, how did things go?

113
00:09:13,575 --> 00:09:18,134
Power Gang sent many killers.

114
00:09:18,134 --> 00:09:24,175
But my place is heavily guarded.
They can't break in.

115
00:09:24,175 --> 00:09:25,975
However...

116
00:09:29,134 --> 00:09:30,934
Speak freely.

117
00:09:33,415 --> 00:09:38,614
They poisoned our only well.

118
00:09:38,614 --> 00:09:43,615
The water reserves will be depleted soon.

119
00:09:46,055 --> 00:09:50,774
I endanger you all. I'm sorry about that.

120
00:09:50,774 --> 00:09:54,494
Madam, no need to apologize.

121
00:09:54,494 --> 00:10:00,134
General Wu's loyal service to the nation
makes him a hero in all our hearts.

122
00:10:00,134 --> 00:10:03,095
Throughout Daxi,

123
00:10:03,095 --> 00:10:07,455
only General Wu deserves to hold the Hero Token.

124
00:10:07,455 --> 00:10:10,575
My family considers it an honor

125
00:10:10,575 --> 00:10:16,095
to ensure your safety this time.

126
00:10:16,095 --> 00:10:19,854
If those villains kidnap you,

127
00:10:19,854 --> 00:10:24,215
it will distract General Wu
and jeopardize frontline operations.

128
00:10:24,215 --> 00:10:27,575
The enemy might take the chance to invade.

129
00:10:27,575 --> 00:10:32,574
If so, we'll become sinners.

130
00:10:35,774 --> 00:10:40,535
Mr. Xiao, just tell me what to do.

131
00:10:40,535 --> 00:10:43,295
I trust you.

132
00:10:43,295 --> 00:10:45,854
The Power Gang poisoned the well

133
00:10:45,854 --> 00:10:49,614
to force us out of this place.

134
00:10:49,614 --> 00:10:55,295
They've likely laid heavy ambushes outside.

135
00:10:55,295 --> 00:10:56,734
Yet according to our arrangement,

136
00:10:56,734 --> 00:11:02,935
we must escort Madam Wu
to meet General Wu in two days.

137
00:11:02,935 --> 00:11:08,774
We can't delay or remain passive.

138
00:11:23,654 --> 00:11:27,614
Father, if some of us leave first,

139
00:11:27,614 --> 00:11:30,815
how long will the remaining water last?

140
00:11:30,815 --> 00:11:33,254
In that case,

141
00:11:33,254 --> 00:11:38,375
the remaining water could sustain us for 20 days.

142
00:11:42,055 --> 00:11:43,855
20 days.

143
00:11:44,575 --> 00:11:46,215
Okay.

144
00:11:46,215 --> 00:11:47,654
I see now.

145
00:11:47,654 --> 00:11:52,894
Listen, we must escort Madam Wu
to meet General Wu on schedule.

146
00:11:52,894 --> 00:11:56,935
Only then can we break this stalemate.

147
00:11:56,935 --> 00:12:01,014
This gives sects time to help us.

148
00:12:01,014 --> 00:12:04,055
United strength can crush the Power Gang

149
00:12:04,055 --> 00:12:06,935
and lift the siege on my family.

150
00:12:06,935 --> 00:12:10,734
But it's dangerous,
and the Power Gang has ruthless killers.

151
00:12:10,734 --> 00:12:15,854
Wouldn't that be risking Madam Wu's life?

152
00:12:15,854 --> 00:12:18,055
Moreover, in the martial world,

153
00:12:18,055 --> 00:12:21,415
who dares oppose the Power Gang?

154
00:12:21,415 --> 00:12:25,415
Your plan sounds delusional.

155
00:12:25,415 --> 00:12:27,815
We just fought the Power Gang.

156
00:12:27,815 --> 00:12:29,335
Have you forgotten?

157
00:12:29,335 --> 00:12:33,175
Can the Power Gang
confront the entire martial circle?

158
00:12:33,175 --> 00:12:37,295
We're all resisters against the Power Gang.

159
00:12:37,295 --> 00:12:43,095
Madam Wu, I swear to protect you with my life.

160
00:12:44,535 --> 00:12:48,254
Hui Shan often spoke of this child.

161
00:12:48,254 --> 00:12:51,574
He truly takes after both of you.

162
00:12:52,614 --> 00:12:54,014
Qiu Shui is right.

163
00:12:54,014 --> 00:12:57,455
We should plan our breakout strategy.

164
00:12:57,455 --> 00:13:02,654
Right now, we're heavily besieged
by the Power Gang.

165
00:13:02,654 --> 00:13:06,095
We can't ensure everyone's safe escape.

166
00:13:06,095 --> 00:13:09,854
True. Breaking out blindly would be disastrous.

167
00:13:09,854 --> 00:13:12,894
Our only advantage

168
00:13:12,894 --> 00:13:16,815
is knowing they target Madam Wu.

169
00:13:16,815 --> 00:13:22,174
How about we use a camouflage?

170
00:13:24,654 --> 00:13:27,494
Have someone impersonate Madam Wu

171
00:13:27,494 --> 00:13:30,934
as bait to mislead them.

172
00:13:33,175 --> 00:13:37,215
To ensure Madam Wu's safe exit,

173
00:13:37,215 --> 00:13:41,654
some of us do diversionary work.

174
00:13:41,654 --> 00:13:42,935
That's it.

175
00:13:42,935 --> 00:13:49,774
The rest will fight tooth and nail
for Madam Wu's safety.

176
00:13:49,774 --> 00:13:56,015
But using someone else as bait for me

177
00:13:56,695 --> 00:13:58,974
sits ill with my conscience.

178
00:13:58,974 --> 00:14:03,135
Madam, let me draw them away.

179
00:14:04,055 --> 00:14:06,055
Qiu Shui.

180
00:14:06,055 --> 00:14:07,520
Mother, don't worry.

181
00:14:07,520 --> 00:14:09,535
Since Yi Ren is away,

182
00:14:09,535 --> 00:14:16,174
it's time for me to do something for the family.

183
00:15:00,894 --> 00:15:05,535
Guys, the Power Gang's atrocities demand action.

184
00:15:05,535 --> 00:15:10,175
We should fight rather than wait for death.

185
00:15:10,175 --> 00:15:15,575
Let's break out and rally allies to destroy them!

186
00:15:15,575 --> 00:15:17,295
- Yes!
- Yes!

187
00:15:17,295 --> 00:15:22,455
Xi Lou, you're injured.
So, you stay and guard Sword Retreat.

188
00:15:22,455 --> 00:15:27,694
We will help Madam Wu
and Qiu Shui break out safely.

189
00:15:30,894 --> 00:15:37,894
This perilous mission demands utmost caution.

190
00:15:37,894 --> 00:15:42,774
I'll await your return with liquor and tea.

191
00:15:42,774 --> 00:15:44,855
- No problem!
- No problem!

192
00:16:00,175 --> 00:16:01,975
Qiu Shui.

193
00:16:03,774 --> 00:16:06,134
Mother.

194
00:16:06,134 --> 00:16:10,694
Countless enemies await outside. Stay vigilant.

195
00:16:11,535 --> 00:16:14,215
Don't worry, Hui Shan.

196
00:16:15,415 --> 00:16:17,455
He has grown up.

197
00:16:17,455 --> 00:16:23,095
He undertakes this mission with a purpose.

198
00:16:23,095 --> 00:16:25,614
Trust his decision.

199
00:16:25,614 --> 00:16:31,774
Our children don't make empty promises.

200
00:16:33,055 --> 00:16:37,654
Father, Mother, I'm sorry
for not spending more time with you.

201
00:16:37,654 --> 00:16:41,014
I promise I'll protect myself.

202
00:16:41,014 --> 00:16:45,975
Besides, I still crave the noodles you cook.

203
00:16:51,734 --> 00:16:53,534
Take this.

204
00:16:54,414 --> 00:16:58,295
Besides the Triple Shameless Moves,
I'm giving you this Lucky Bag.

205
00:16:58,295 --> 00:17:02,414
It contains trap mechanisms.
Remember how to use them.

206
00:17:02,414 --> 00:17:04,615
Fight enemies ruthlessly with them.

207
00:17:08,934 --> 00:17:11,894
She's right.

208
00:17:11,894 --> 00:17:16,454
I've fallen for her traps before.

209
00:17:19,694 --> 00:17:22,055
I deserve it.

210
00:17:23,174 --> 00:17:24,815
Qiu Shui.

211
00:17:24,815 --> 00:17:27,535
When we drank earlier,

212
00:17:27,535 --> 00:17:31,575
you said you envied righteous heroes

213
00:17:31,575 --> 00:17:35,255
because they could eliminate the evil
and help the weak.

214
00:17:35,255 --> 00:17:39,095
But think about it.

215
00:17:39,095 --> 00:17:45,174
Flesh-and-blood mortals should fear death.

216
00:17:45,174 --> 00:17:51,694
But why does righteousness make them fearless?

217
00:17:54,894 --> 00:18:01,734
Because some things surpass life itself.

218
00:18:02,694 --> 00:18:04,694
Look what happened today.

219
00:18:04,694 --> 00:18:11,894
Many people are willing to bleed
and die for our family.

220
00:18:11,894 --> 00:18:14,375
Remember this forever.

221
00:18:15,295 --> 00:18:18,375
Father, Mother.

222
00:18:19,575 --> 00:18:21,975
I will remember.

223
00:18:21,975 --> 00:18:24,295
After Madam Wu's safe escape,

224
00:18:24,295 --> 00:18:29,934
I'll seek help from Jinzhong's sects
to jointly repel the Power Gang.

225
00:18:35,214 --> 00:18:37,014
Go now.

226
00:18:42,214 --> 00:18:45,535
Stay safe. You must stay safe.

227
00:18:52,055 --> 00:18:54,694
Father, Mother.

228
00:18:54,694 --> 00:19:01,135
Within 20 days, I'll surely gather aid
to rescue Sword Retreat.

229
00:19:04,295 --> 00:19:06,095
Take care.

230
