00:20:02,096 --> 00:20:07,184
 ♫ How brief this mortal journey goes ♫ 

244
00:20:07,184 --> 00:20:09,328
 ♫ The bleak wind starts to blow ♫ 

245
00:20:09,328 --> 00:20:14,671
 ♫ Like a mournful farewell ode ♫ 

246
00:20:14,671 --> 00:20:17,454
 ♫ When zither breaks, who'll sing along ♫ 

247
00:20:17,454 --> 00:20:20,815
Hui Shan, don't be sad.

248
00:20:22,055 --> 00:20:25,575
Our son's grown into a responsible man.

249
00:20:25,575 --> 00:20:29,255
Look, he has so many

250
00:20:30,208 --> 00:20:35,894
courageous and loyal friends.

251
00:20:35,894 --> 00:20:41,855
We should trust him
and let him roam the martial world.

252
00:20:42,894 --> 00:20:44,775
Stop crying.

253
00:20:47,894 --> 00:20:51,055
I just want one last look at him.

254
00:21:10,414 --> 00:21:12,214
Go!

255
00:21:21,335 --> 00:21:24,095
 After breaking out, we'll split into four groups. 

256
00:21:24,095 --> 00:21:27,775
 Mr. Qu, Mr. Meng and Ironclad Constable
will lead the Group Dragon as a decoy, 

257
00:21:27,775 --> 00:21:31,095
 buying escape time for the other three groups. 

258
00:21:31,095 --> 00:21:34,095
 Madam Wu will hide under a black hat. 

