265
00:22:29,535 --> 00:22:31,335
This way!

266
00:22:44,654 --> 00:22:47,934
 Tang Fang, Feng Lang, guard Madam Wu
with the Group Phoenix. 

267
00:22:47,934 --> 00:22:49,414
 Break through the eastern woods. 

268
00:22:49,414 --> 00:22:51,514
 Remember to wear gas masks. 

269
00:22:51,514 --> 00:22:53,295
 You'll pass through the poisonous forest. 

270
00:22:53,295 --> 00:22:55,374
