 In this case, let me draw you all here. 

279
00:24:28,614 --> 00:24:30,414
Go!

280
00:24:34,255 --> 00:24:36,495
 Tang Rou, Yu Han, Zuo Qiu, proceed cautiously. 

281
00:24:36,495 --> 00:24:38,055
 Find a chance to head uphill. 

282
00:24:38,055 --> 00:24:41,615
 Power Gang won't expect
you'd head in the opposite direction. 

283
00:24:47,134 --> 00:24:48,934
Go.

284
00:25:04,614 --> 00:25:08,414
Leave Madam Wu, and I'll spare you.

285
