288
00:25:21,535 --> 00:25:23,894
Let's see.

289
00:25:23,894 --> 00:25:25,694
Attack!

290
00:26:14,255 --> 00:26:16,055
Don't!

291
00:26:21,735 --> 00:26:23,855
Run now!

292
00:26:24,815 --> 00:26:26,975
Go!

293
00:26:26,975 --> 00:26:30,575
