295
00:26:39,614 --> 00:26:42,015
Leave!

296
00:26:42,015 --> 00:26:44,134
Come on! Let's go!

297
00:26:44,134 --> 00:26:47,775
- Young Master, go!
- Let's go together!

298
00:26:49,775 --> 00:26:51,575
Come on. Get up.

299
00:26:53,374 --> 00:26:58,775
Your family protected me before.
Today, I repay you.

300
00:26:58,775 --> 00:27:00,614
Enough! Let's go!

301
00:27:00,614 --> 00:27:02,855
Leave!

302
00:27:06,335 --> 00:27:09,095
Young Master, run!

303
00:27:26,335 --> 00:27:28,135
Kong Yang Qin!

304
00:27:29,654 --> 00:27:32,335
You're way below Fu Tian Yi.

305
00:27:33,934 --> 00:27:36,495
You can't kill me!

306
00:27:36,495 --> 00:27:38,815
You can't kill me!

307
00:28:11,894 --> 00:28:14,654
Xiao Qiu Shui's gadgets work well.

308
00:28:16,095 --> 00:28:19,854
- This is...
- Anti-poison gear. Take it.

309
00:28:19,854 --> 00:28:22,895
Take one each. Safety first. Wear it.

310
00:28:33,894 --> 00:28:36,694
- Protect Madam Wu!
- Yes!

311
00:29:27,894 --> 00:29:30,214
