312
00:29:40,055 --> 00:29:41,894
What's going on? Where's Madam Wu?

313
00:29:41,894 --> 00:29:45,535
I don't know. Mr. Qiu Shui
told me to dress like this.

314
00:29:45,535 --> 00:29:48,185
 
 Father, Mother, though Qiu's dead, 

315
00:29:48,185 --> 00:29:52,654
 Power Gang's cunning with many spies. 

316
00:29:52,654 --> 00:29:58,254
