and leave with Feng Lang. 

318
00:30:02,934 --> 00:30:04,654
 Should we inform Mr. Feng? 

319
00:30:04,654 --> 00:30:07,614
 - No need.
- Yes. 

320
00:30:07,614 --> 00:30:11,015
 Then what about the real Madam Wu? 

321
00:30:11,015 --> 00:30:14,214
