about Madam Wu's whereabouts.

330
00:30:57,495 --> 00:30:59,454
Doesn't that seem suspicious?

331
00:31:01,174 --> 00:31:06,254
Lady Tang, may I think you came
to the Xiao's for ulterior motives?

332
00:31:12,174 --> 00:31:14,815
Why did you save me earlier?

333
00:31:14,815 --> 00:31:18,014
For no reason. It's no big deal.

334
00:31:42,975 --> 00:31:46,535
Run! Why did you stop running?

335
00:31:49,055 --> 00:31:55,015
Let me carve your bones into guqin picks.

336
00:31:55,015 --> 00:31:57,414
Fine.

337
00:31:57,414 --> 00:31:59,214
I won't run anymore.

338
00:32:00,454 --> 00:32:02,974
So, are you afraid of death?

339
00:32:04,174 --> 00:32:05,974
Not exactly.

340
00:32:07,694 --> 00:32:10,014
I'm going to kill you.

341
00:32:11,535 --> 00:32:14,615
- Kill him.
- Yes.

342
00:33:08,614 --> 00:33:11,335
You killed the disciples of my family.

343
00:33:12,654 --> 00:33:16,694
Play your guqin in the underworld.

344
00:33:29,335 --> 00:33:33,214
This cheap trick will get you killed.

345
00:33:34,015 --> 00:33:36,374
The fun is just beginning.

346
00:33:36,374 --> 00:33:38,335
Tell me about Madam Wu's whereabouts.

347
00:33:38,335 --> 00:33:42,295
Otherwise, I'll feed your flesh
to my poison insects?

348
00:33:43,694 --> 00:33:48,694
 Hua Gu Fen, the Poison Demon,
this place shall be your grave. 

349
00:34:26,214 --> 00:34:30,774
 Tang Rou, you're excelled
in hidden weapons and mechanisms. 

350
00:34:30,774 --> 00:34:33,895
 So, do me a small favor. 

351
00:34:34,694 --> 00:34:37,094
