Let me neutralize the toxin.

361
00:35:54,334 --> 00:35:56,134
No need.

362
00:35:57,015 --> 00:36:01,535
Xue Yu gave me antidotes.

363
00:36:01,535 --> 00:36:04,454
I'll take one later.

364
00:36:06,654 --> 00:36:09,134
What about Madam Wu and Tang Rou?

365
00:36:09,134 --> 00:36:13,134
They should be safe by now.

366
00:36:13,134 --> 00:36:15,694
 Tang Rou, escort Madam Wu and Master Zhang 

367
00:36:15,694 --> 00:36:19,294
