369
00:36:20,975 --> 00:36:23,255
 Don't worry. I have a method. 

370
00:36:34,134 --> 00:36:37,335
Remarkable! This stuff actually helped us fly!

371
00:36:39,415 --> 00:36:41,694
Madam Wu.

372
00:36:41,694 --> 00:36:44,455
Madam Wu, are you okay?

373
00:36:44,455 --> 00:36:46,575
I'm good.

374
00:36:46,575 --> 00:36:50,574
